  <p>Input-2 <br />
<strong>“23four5six7”</strong> <br />
Output-2 <br />
<strong>234567</strong></p>
</blockquote>

<blockquote>
  <p>Input-3 <br />
<strong>“2three45sixseven”</strong> <br />
Output-3 <br />
<strong>234567</strong></p>
</blockquote>

<blockquote>
  <p>Input-4 <br />
<strong>123</strong> <br />
Output-4 <br />
<strong>123</strong></p>
